      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the plastic trim pieces. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
