      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so it's spotless inside and out with zero issues. It drives like a total dream! I'm looking to find it a great new home quickly to help build my seller profile, so come grab a total gem at a fantastic price. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
