    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a concours-level E46 M3, a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering prowess. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing, both of which have been meticulously serviced. This unit delivers a linear power band through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate fatigue, and the suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with fresh bushings and dampers. Finished in Titanium Silver with an immaculate Nappa leather interior, the vehicle exhibits zero clear coat failure or interior bolster wear. This is a turn-key collector's piece with a documented service history addressing all major preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
